title: Is the case of the United States COVID-19 the highest worldwide because of the "great test "?
subtitle: If the virus does not spread, the rate of positive COVID-19 test results will not increase. Unfortunately, the rate has risen.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: The reason that the United States documented most of the cases of COVID-19 in the world in 2020 is that it tested more people at a faster rate than any other country.
